Subject: New License Not Showing Up

I received the license via Email by our distributor and the information that we can download the software via netwrix.com. I logged into netwrix.com with the same email the product was bought for (w.schober@sec-consult.com) Sadly my product list is empty and i cannot download Pingcastle.
